Date: 1995-03-02

Title: Two dimensional QCD and abelian bosonization

Authors: Marco Bochicchio

Comments: paper revised, several signs and coefficients corrected. A comment on

regularization dependence and several references addedJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B356 (1995) 337-340

A bosonized action, that reproduces the structure of the 't Hooft equationfor $QCD_2$ in the large-$N$ limit, up to regularization dependent terms, isderived.